mcp-ollama-python for Debian
=============================

Packaging Notes
===============

This package uses pyproject.toml for build configuration and pybuild-plugin-pyproject
for building. The source format is 3.0 (native).

Full source code and build information is available at:
  https://github.com/pblagoje/mcp-ollama-python

Building
========

The standard Debian build process applies:
  dpkg-buildpackage -rfakeroot

Or using gbp (git-buildpackage):
  gbp buildpackage

Dependencies
============

Build dependencies are defined in debian/control.

Tests are run via autopkgtest (debian/tests/control):
  python3 -m pytest tests/
